{
  "stem": "443.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody had to go to a central bathhouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where I started to help out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and this is how it continued till the end, till we were gathered to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Until then, we had freedom to go around the streets, but we did have to wear a star to let everybody know who are, so we should be recognized.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It only-- while-- while the-- we were under the Romanian occupation, it wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then we became occupied in 1940 from the Hungarians, that's when we realized that they're not the same-- the situation wasn't the same.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While they were trying to-- trying to call the Jews by their names, and my father used to say, those are not the Hungarian [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Hungarians, they have whiskers, so their-- their expression that they used to use that the Hungarians are the whiskers, the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These are not the same [NON-ENGLISH] that I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because my father was really born in a small town, it was only Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's all there was is Hungarian-- Hungarian Gentiles and Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they lived peacefully.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Hungarians came in and start screaming dirty Jew, that's where my father realized this is not right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [SIGHS] normal life continued.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People had stores.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People went to work, whoever had work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then when the Germans came in, that's when the real trouble started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when was that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 19-- in 1943, they came into our city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember vividly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Thursday.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was March-- March the 15th.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't-- I mean, we didn't know what was really going on in the world, because we had no radios in the house.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
